  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Children from 6 months to 6 years are randomly allocated into AuraGain group or I-gel group.
      After anesthetic induction without neuromuscular blocking agent, assigned device in inserted
      by skillful anesthesiologist. The outcome measures are recorded and analysed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
